OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA wet and windy day as rain
OL,6,Fspreads across the region, turning
OL,7,Flocally heavy at times, particularly
OL,8,Fover the hills. Feeling muggy under
OL,9,Fwidespread cloud cover and hill fog.
OL,10,FGusty winds, particularly from mid-
OL,11,Fafternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FOutbreaks of rain becoming
OL,14,Fincreasingly showery into the evening,
OL,15,Fhowever heavy bursts are still
OL,16,Fpossible, especially over the high
OL,17,Fground of Cumbria. Widely windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
